So excited to share our love story exclusively through our friends at @vogueaustralia. It was honestly the most magical day marrying my best friend and soul mate, @shaun.lyle, and their are no words to describe how overwhelming it was to have all of our favourite people in one room. Too many people to thank and details to share so read all about our incredible day on Vogue now.. they will fill you in on all the goss! (link in bio)
